snippet.title: Geethanjali Kids - Rhymes and Stories
snippet.description:
Geethanjali Kids - Rhymes and Stories is filled with all the popular Fairy Tales, Bedtime Stories, Nursery Rhymes, Lullabies and lots more educational content. Enjoy the best quality entertainment for babies, toddlers and kids.

Must watch our popular videos: Rapunzel, Cinderella, Sleeping Beauty,  Pinocchio, Beauty and the Beast , Thumbelina, Hansel and Gretel, Rumpelstiltskin, Jack and the beanstalk, The Gingerbread Man,Goldilocks and the Three Bears, Little Red Riding Hood, Nursery Rhymes, Learn Alphabets, Learn Colors and More!
